{"tid":1085268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚇！樹上開滿了「支那蝗后」","createTime":"2019-03-31T04:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T05:49:00.000Z","uid":32511,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9afb21695434d8ef6031b254b7ba6068cd6a708a","tid":1085268,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:51:42.000Z","msg":"春暖花開，又到了賞櫻季節，但中國遊客在拍照時爬樹和摘花早已備受詬病。據港媒報導，近日有中國網友上載圖片，圖中所見樹上開滿的並非花朵，而是「中國大媽」。<br />\n <br />\n據《星島日報》報導，據稱，大媽們趁着春天鳥語花香的好時節都到戶外郊遊，但見周圍景色優美，隨即拿出手機拍照。可是大媽們為求拍出「新穎」照片，竟爬到樹上，一個見狀，其他人亦爭相模仿，甚至有人搖晃樹枝，造成花瓣飄落的「美景」以供拍照。<br />\n <br />\n不少網友也表示，這種賞花方式不僅不美觀，而且十分危險。「你並不是在賞花，而是在傷花！嚴重的還會受到處罰。」<br />\n <br />\n大自然需要大家共同愛護，不要因一時之快，罔顧文明和安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mg2zRrD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMg2zRrD.png&h=871c34b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oojKudk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoojKudk.png&h=708bb029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e97d5ca4dff63cad1d30f96f81e73446f5542eff","tid":1085268,"uid":47080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"咁矮跌佢哋唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c637a639b7a5ec276dbe587c38df2c09abb9f1d","tid":1085268,"uid":14244,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:58:59.000Z","msg":"人型蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6e1f4513ea5871ce7cd6b21c1a4c9c28dc323c","tid":1085268,"uid":39550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾民族"},{"pid":"eeb916d0bb9fe2da314d6788ae15ffed89b72f54","tid":1085268,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:29:36.000Z","msg":"好唔明支那人嘅美學觀"},{"pid":"1c42d5ec2932c2bc349ac169650128d8865eef22","tid":1085268,"uid":194012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eeb916d0bb9fe2da314d6788ae15ffed89b72f54",